AUDIENCE: It sounds like you
have a lot of great recipes

00:40:20.960 --> 00:40:22.049
that aren't just baking.

00:40:22.049 --> 00:40:24.340
Are you going to write another
cookbook with your pizza

00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:25.798
and gnocchi and
